headline: POSCO and JSW Sign an Agreement to Explore Steel Plant in India
summary: PKX and JSW Steel team up for a proposed 50:50 joint venture to explore a 6 MTPA integrated steel plant in India, eyeing Odisha as a preferred site.

headline: Eastman Partners With Huafon to Build New Yarn Facility in China
summary: EMN teams up with Huafon to launch a new facility in China, boosting Naia yarn output and advancing sustainable textile innovation.
